01:08:05.782 --> 01:08:07.382
Um...

01:08:07.384 --> 01:08:08.716
Honeybun, the bad guy is coming.

01:08:14.491 --> 01:08:15.790
Let's get the fuck
out of here, eh?

01:08:15.792 --> 01:08:17.591
