do everything around here?

01:08:46.323 --> 01:08:47.622
Where is he?

01:08:52.629 --> 01:08:54.328
Where the fuck did he go?

01:08:54.331 --> 01:08:56.663
You blew out
my fucking eardrums.

01:08:56.666 --> 01:08:58.399
Shit. I'm sorry, honeybun.

01:08:58.401 --> 01:09:01.202
